column5: Just returned from a 7 day stay stay with Lac Seul Airways/ Amik outposts. Group of 4 caught and released 1400 walleye, numerous fish from 23 to 26 inches, the biggest being 27 1/4 inches weighing 5lb 9oz Largest pike was 36 inches weighing 10 lbs. Had a wonderful time. Recommend this operation to anyone.
Thanks for the post Kyle, always nice to hear positive comments!
